[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0427","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0427.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0242","title":"Slackware Linux POP3 邮件文件未授权访问漏洞","description":"部分 Linux 系统（如 Slackware）的 POP3 邮件服务存在认证绕过漏洞，当系统启用影子密码（shadow passwords）时，POP3 守护进程未能正确验证用户凭证，远程攻击者无需有效账号即可通过 POP3 协议访问目标系统上的邮件文件，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击复杂度低，危害较大。受影响系统包括使用 shadow passwords 机制的早期 Linux 发行版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0242"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.133","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 的 POP3 守护进程 (如 popper) 到已修复版本，或禁用 POP3 服务改用 IMAP+SSL。确保 /etc/shadow 文件权限为 400 且仅 root 可读，避免使用未加密的 POP3 协议传输密码。如系统已不再维护，建议迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0242","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0242.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0242","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0242.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80898/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0427.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0420","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0420.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0235","title":"NCSA httpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA httpd 1.4.1 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标 Web 服务器发送特制请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 系列版本，攻击者利用此漏洞可完全控制受影响系统，危害严重。目前官方已停止维护该软件，建议用户升级至其他受支持的 Web 服务器软件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0235"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.270","remediation":"NCSA httpd 已停止维护多年，官方不再发布安全更新。建议立即迁移至 Apache HTTP Server（最新稳定版为 2.4.68），该服务器由 NCSA httpd 衍生而来，兼容原有配置且持续提供安全支持。迁移后注意关闭不必要的 CGI 脚本并配置最低权限运行服务进程以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0235","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0235","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0235.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-73j6-752c-7hrj/GHSA-73j6-752c-7hrj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ed289855-2ebf-495d-9754-266d2c9ea1e7.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0420.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0417","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0417.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0232","title":"NCSA HTTPD 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.5c 版本在处理 HTTP 请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送超长或特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致远程代码执行或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.5c 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，且无需认证即可利用。由于该软件已停止维护，建议用户迁移至 Apache httpd 等受支持的 Web 服务器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0232"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.893","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 NCSA HTTPd 1.5c，无官方补丁。建议立即迁移至活跃维护的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制对 80/TCP 端口的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0232","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0232.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0232","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0232.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83083/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0417.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0189","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0189.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0077","title":"Linux Kernel 2.2 TCP 初始序列号可预测漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2 版本 TCP 协议栈存在 TCP 初始序列号（ISN）可预测漏洞，远程攻击者可通过预测目标系统 TCP 连接的初始序列号，伪造 TCP 数据包实施会话劫持或欺骗攻击，导致未经授权的数据访问或服务中断。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.2 系列内核，攻击者只需掌握目标连接的序列号生成规律即可利用，无需身份认证。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0077"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.603","remediation":"建议升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.26 以上版本，或迁移至 2.4.x/2.6.x 系列内核以获得 RFC 1948 TCP ISN 随机化支持。如无法升级内核，可通过 `echo 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/tcp_syncookies` 启用 SYN Cookies 缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/139"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0189.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0556","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0556.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0337","title":"IBM AIX batch queue (bsh) 本地和远程权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统的批处理队列（bsh）存在权限提升漏洞。当网络打印服务启用时，本地或远程攻击者可通过向批处理队列提交特制任务，利用不充分的权限控制机制获取超出授权的系统访问权限，导致攻击者能够执行任意命令或操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 AIX 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0337"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.850","remediation":"立即安装 IBM 针对 AIX batch queue (bsh) 的安全补丁，升级到 AIX 4.3.3 及更高修复版本。如无法打补丁，可通过 `chsubserver -r bsh` 禁用 bsh 网络打印服务，或在 `/etc/security/user` 中限制 bsh 可执行权限仅为 root 用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0337","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0337","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0337.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/Wollny/CVE-1999-0337.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r76x-g7v4-r3c6/GHSA-r76x-g7v4-r3c6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000050.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6dd5b793-7342-42d5-867d-37abc515d322.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0556.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0660","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0660.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0423","title":"HP HP-UX hpterm 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.20 系统中的 hpterm 终端模拟器存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 hpterm 发送特制请求利用该漏洞，从而获取额外的系统权限。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地访问权限，利用条件相对有限，影响 HP-UX 10.20 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级到不受影响的版本或应用厂商发布的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0423"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.910","remediation":"建议升级至 HP-UX 11.0 及以上版本，或安装 HP 发布的 PHSS_19011 补丁。如无法升级，执行 `chmod 755 /usr/bin/hpterm` 移除 hpterm 的 setuid 位，或通过 `chmod 0` 禁用该程序作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9903-093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0660.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0256","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0256.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0113","title":"IBM AIX rlogin 权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 3.2.5 的 rlogin 实现中存在参数注入漏洞（CWE-88），当向 rlogin 命令传入 `-froot` 参数时，未经授权的本地攻击者可利用该参数绕过正常的身份认证机制，以 root 权限直接登录目标系统，实现权限提升。该漏洞源于程序未对命令行参数进行有效过滤和消毒，攻击者无需知道目标用户密码即可获取系统最高控制权。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 3.2.5 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0113"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1994-05-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.820","remediation":"建议立即升级 IBM AIX 至 4.1.0 及以上版本（该漏洞已在 AIX 4.x 中修复），或安装对应 APAR 补丁。同时禁用 rlogin/rsh/r-commands 系列服务（注释 /etc/inetd.conf 中相关行并重启 inetd），迁移至 OpenSSH 替代远程管理。限制 root 远程登录，在 /etc/securetty 中移除不必要的终端，并启用 PAM 认证机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/458","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19348","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0113","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0113.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/604.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/rlogin_froot.nasl","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/609.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/murahari1/recon-tool/blob/f63a205225373d0d87b081758c11899777970b0f/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0256.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0266","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0266.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0120","title":"Sun Solaris utmp 文件本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中 utmp 文件存在权限配置不当漏洞。当该文件被设置为非 root 用户可写时，本地攻击者可修改 utmp 文件内容，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS/Solaris 系统，需要攻击者拥有本地账户权限，攻击者可通过构造特制的 utmp 记录实现权限提升，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0120"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-03-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.890","remediation":"确保 utmp 文件仅 root 可写：执行 `chmod 644 /var/adm/utmp` 或 `chmod 644 /etc/utmp` 移除其他用户的写权限，同时 `chown root:root /var/adm/utmp` 确保文件属主为 root。升级到已修复此问题的 SunOS/Solaris 安全补丁版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/126"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0266.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0557","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0557.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0338","title":"IBM AIX 性能工具本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统的许可软件产品性能工具存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该工具集的特权配置缺陷，通过执行特定命令获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限即可利用，无需用户交互。成功利用后攻击者可完全控制系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0338"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-02-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.000","remediation":"安装 IBM 针对该漏洞发布的 AIX APAR 补丁包，或升级至包含该修复的最新 AIX 维护级别（Maintenance Level）。临时缓解措施：以 root 用户执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/filemon /usr/bin/svmon /usr/bin/tprof` 移除受影响性能工具的 setuid 权限，并限制非授信用户对性能工具目录的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0338"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0557.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0397","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0397.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0211","title":"Sun Solaris NFS mountd 导出列表过长致权限绕过漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统中 NFS mount 守护进程存在访问控制绕过漏洞。当 NFS 导出列表条目超过 256 字符时，守护进程未能正确处理超长字符串，导致所有访问控制检查失效。远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可挂载本应受限的 NFS 目录，从而非法访问敏感文件。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.x 及 Solaris 早期版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0211"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.270","remediation":"安装 Sun 针对对应操作系统版本的安全补丁：SunOS 4.1.3/4.1.3_U1 安装补丁 101945-xx，Solaris 2.3 安装补丁 101358-xx，Solaris 2.4 安装补丁 101945-xx。无法立即打补丁时，将 /etc/exports 中每条导出条目控制在 256 字符以内，使用主机名/IP 而非 netgroup 进行访问控制，并在 NFS 服务端防火墙限制仅允许可信网络访问 portmap（111/tcp,111/udp）和 nfsd（2049/tcp,2049/udp）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/24","https://vuls.cert.org/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=96665790","https://vuls.cert.org/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=97124517","https://vuls.cert.org/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=97124527"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0397.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0362","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0362.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0181","title":"Unix rpc.walld 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"rpc.walld（wall daemon）是 Unix 系统中用于向所有在线终端广播消息的 RPC 服务，默认通过 rpc 协议监听网络请求。该服务存在访问控制缺陷，未授权远程攻击者无需认证即可向其发送特制 RPC 请求，向所有登录用户终端广播虚假消息，导致拒绝服务或社会工程攻击。部分实现中攻击者还可利用调试功能或命令行注入执行任意远程命令。该漏洞影响 Solaris、HP-UX 等 Unix 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0181"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.403","remediation":"禁用 rpc.walld 服务（如不需全局广播功能），或通过 tcpwrappers 在 /etc/hosts.deny 添加 `walld: ALL` 限制访问来源。各 UNIX 厂商（如 Sun、HP、IBM）曾发布对应补丁，建议查阅原厂安全公告获取对应修复包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0181"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0362.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0550","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0550.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0334","title":"Sun Solaris fsck 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.2 和 2.3 系统中，fsck（文件系统一致性检查）在系统启动过程中执行失败后，系统会降级至单用户维护模式，此时拥有物理访问权限的本地用户无需认证即可直接获取 root shell 权限。该漏洞属于本地权限提升漏洞，攻击者须具备物理接触目标主机的条件，通过在系统引导阶段触发 fsck 检查失败来利用此问题，进而完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，影响 Solaris 2.2 及 2.3 版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0334"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1993-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.570","remediation":"升级到 Solaris 2.4 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，应限制物理访问，确保控制台仅授权人员可用，并在系统启动时值守以防止 fsck 被交互式劫持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0334"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0550.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0298","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0298.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0145","title":"Sendmail WIZ 命令远程权限提升漏洞","description":"Sendmail WIZ 命令漏洞存在于 sendmail 邮件服务器软件中，其 DEBUG 模式的 WIZ 命令默认开启且未经身份认证。远程攻击者可直接连接至 SMTP 端口（25/TCP），发送 WIZ 命令后输入 root 即可获得目标系统最高权限，实现完全控制。该漏洞影响早期版本 sendmail，危害严重，攻击门槛极低，无需任何前置条件即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0145"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1993-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.620","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.6.10 或更新版本（该版本已移除 WIZ 调试命令），或在 sendmail.cf 中注释或移除 `Ow` 相关 WIZ 选项来禁用 WIZ 命令。若无法立即升级，应在防火墙上限制对 TCP 25 端口的访问，仅允许可信来源连接 SMTP 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2019/Jun/16","http://www.alw.nih.gov/Security/Docs/admin-guide-to-cracking.101.html","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1990-11.html","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1993-14.html","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/05/4","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/06/1","http://www2.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1995_1/0332.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0298.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0270","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0270.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0124","title":"UMN Gopher 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"UMN Gopher 及 Gopher+ 服务程序（1.12 和 2.0x 版本）存在未授权任意文件读取漏洞。由于 gopherd 守护进程未能对文件访问请求进行充分的权限校验，攻击者可以利用该缺陷绕过访问限制，读取 gopher 守护进程可访问范围内的任意系统文件，包括敏感配置信息。此漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，攻击难度低，对系统机密性构成严重威胁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0124"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1993-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.420","remediation":"升级 UMN gopher 至 2.0.18 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。同时修改 gopherd 配置文件，设置根目录为仅含公开内容的隔离路径（如 /var/gopher），并使用 chroot 机制限制守护进程访问范围。通过文件系统权限确保 gopher 运行用户（如 nobody）对 /etc/passwd 等敏感文件无读取权限。如无需对外提供 Gopher 服务，建议直接停止并卸载 gopherd。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0124"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0270.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0401","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0401.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0214","title":"Sun SunOS 4.1 ICMP Unreachable 报文拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Microsystems SunOS 4.1/4.1.1/4.1.2 操作系统存在 ICMP 不可达数据包处理缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标主机发送伪造的 ICMP Unreachable 数据包，导致目标系统内核错误地关闭受影响 TCP 连接，造成合法服务中断。该漏洞影响所有运行上述版本 SunOS 的系统，攻击门槛低、危害较大。厂商已发布相应补丁修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0214"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1992-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.663","remediation":"升级 SunOS 至 4.1.3 或更高版本，该版本修复了 ICMP Unreachable 报文处理逻辑。在网络边界防火墙配置规则，过滤外部传入的伪造 ICMP 不可达数据包。如系统仍在使用且无法升级，可考虑迁移至受支持的 Solaris 版本。禁用不必要的 ICMP 响应功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0214"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0401.toml"}]